1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
Science has a clearer story about rainbows than social media does.

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:07,200
When light hits water droplets, magic happens.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:09,200
But it’s all about physics.

4
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:12,000
Every color bends at a different angle.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:14,400
That’s why you see the spectrum.

6
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:17,600
Red shines at 42 degrees, violet at 40.3.

7
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:20,400
That’s how you get a rainbow arc.

8
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:25,600
Rainbows are nature’s art, but they follow strict rules of light and water.

